# Default-deny the build context so local traces, credentials, VCS metadata,
# tests, caches, and developer files are never sent to the Docker daemon.
**

# Runtime root files.
!server.py
!requirements.txt
!LICENSE
!NOTICE

# Runtime source and static assets.
!analyzer/
!analyzer/**
!anthill/
!anthill/**
!tracer/
!tracer/**
!static/
!static/**
!samples/
!samples/**

# Keep generated Python artifacts out even inside allowlisted directories.
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*.pyd
**/*.so
